  "original_lang": "ta",
  "original_title": "\u0b95\u0ba8\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bbe\u0b9f\u0bc1 \u0baa\u0bc1\u0ba9\u0bb0\u0bcd\u0bb5\u0bbe\u0bb4\u0bcd\u0bb5\u0bc1 \u0ba8\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bc8\u0baf\u00a0 \u0b95\u0bc8\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0baf\u0bbf\u0ba9\u0bcd \u0b95\u0bca\u0bb2\u0bc8 : \u0bb5\u0baf\u0bb0\u0bcd, \u0bae\u0bc2\u0b99\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0baa\u0bca\u0bb2\u0bcd\u0bb2\u0bc1\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bcd \u0bae\u0bc0\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bc1 : \u0b95\u0bc8\u0ba4\u0bbe\u0ba9\u00a0 4\u00a0 \u0baa\u0b9f\u0bc8\u0baf\u0bbf\u0ba9\u0bb0\u0bc1\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc1\u0bae\u0bcd \u0bb5\u0bbf\u0bb3\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bae\u0bb1\u0bbf\u0baf\u0bb2\u0bcd",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Murder of a prisoner in Kantakadu Rehabilitation Center: Wire, bamboo poles rescue: All 4 arrested soldiers remanded",
      "author": "",
      "body_lines": [
        "Four constables who acted as counselors of the station have been arrested in connection with the incident in which a prisoner was allegedly beaten to death at Kantakadu Rehabilitation Central Station under Polonnaruwa \u2013 Welikanda Police Division.",
        "Police Spokesperson Senior Police Inspector Nihal Talduwa said that Welikanda Police arrested two army and two air force personnel in connection with the suspicious death of the 35-year-old prisoner from Badulai-Hali Ela-Temodarai area.",
        "Also, according to the source of the said four, the police have also seized the wire and bamboo sticks believed to have been used to attack the prisoner, said Senior Superintendent of Police Nihal Taltuwa.",
        "A 35-year-old from Kottapitiya and a 36-year-old from Navalapitiya, Air Force sergeant-rank officers on duty as counselors at the Kanthakadu Rehabilitation Center, were among those arrested.",
        "Police said that one of the arrested military officers is a stop sergeant aged 39 years from Kalnewa area and the other is a sergeant grade officer aged 37 years from Hurikaswewa.",
        "The suspects were produced in the Polonnaruwa Magistrate's Court yesterday (2) on charges of assault and murder. The judge ordered them to be remanded until the 14th.",
        "Meanwhile, after the incident, a large number of prisoners who were detained at the Central Rehabilitation Center on June 29 had escaped.",
        "When the incident took place, 998 inmates who were being rehabilitated for drug addiction were detained at the Kantakadu Rehabilitation Center, Commissioner General of Rehabilitation, Major General Darshana Hettirachchi said.",
        "723 of them had escaped from there. 679 of them have been arrested till today (2) and have been produced in the court and have been kept in remand.",
        "At present only 272 people are detained in the Kandha forest camp under rehabilitation activities.",
        "Police Spokesman Senior Superintendent of Police Nihal Talduwa said that a special investigation is being conducted in connection with the suspicious death of a prisoner and the escape of prisoners who were detained on court orders.",
        "It is to be noted that these investigations are being conducted under the supervision of Polonnaruwa Senior Police Inspector Oshan Hewawittharana under Welikanda Police Officer-in-Charge Chief Police Inspector Samantha Ratnayake."
      ],
